SlateDB fleet manager

Usage: sleet <COMMAND>

Commands:
  run       Run the fleet daemon
  status    Show fleet nodes, service assignments, and service health, derived from object storage
  db        Inspect and edit the databases in a fleet spec
  validate  Parse and validate a fleet spec
  schema    Print a JSON Schema
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
